Hi,
I currently used LongRunningTask inspired by this example: https://answers.atlassian.com/questions/23948/how-to-create-a-progress-bar
After implementing my own task, I encountered the problem, that the progress bar wasn't updated. I figured out, that this was related to the fact, that I used progress.setStatus(""); to set an empty status. I had to change it to something else than an empty string to get die UI refreshed.

...
progress.setStatus(" "); // if empty, ui update fails
int count = 0;
int userCount = users.size();
progress.setTotalObjects(userCount);
...
for (User user : users) {
    count += 1;
    progress.setPercentage(count, userCount);
    ...
}

